{
  "texts": [
    "Nonetheless, several formal prompt approaches have been proposed, along with circumstances under which certain styles are expected to be more effective.",
    "Importantly, we note that prior research into the effectiveness of LLMs in completing assessments has primarily focused on finding one prompt that seemed to work well, then using that prompt for generating all responses.",
    "There are reasons to suspect, however, that candidates that use an LLM to assist with a test, may employ a variety of different prompt approaches.",
    "First, the popular literature on LLMs and Generative AI includes considerable discourse on the topic of prompt engineering.",
    "Second, many websites offering career advisory services (e.g., resume writing) provide advice to job seekers about the importance of effective prompting when using a LLM to assist with writing job application materials."
  ]
}